description.en: Influxcoin is a PoW/PoS coin that uses that X11 hashing algorithm during its PoW stage. There is no pre-mine and beginners can mine using their CPU and GPU. Influxcoin was initially planned as a coin to teach youngsters about cryptocurrency but has since evolved to a bigger project.
